init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien is trying to get home, but he's not sure how.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Well, you're the only person I know who's been to space and back, so I'm hoping you can help me," said

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Yes, but that was just a movie," Matt Damon replied.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt Damon and the alien met with the scientists at NASA, where they were given a tour of the facility.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I know you guys are working on a way to get to Mars, and I was hoping you could help us," Matt Damon told the scientists

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I know, but he's not here to be studied, he's here to get home," Matt Damon replied.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt Damon and the alien were given a tour of the ship, which was built to withstand the harsh conditions of space.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien, in turn, thanked Matt Damon for everything he had done for him.
